DialogueNode.dialogue: Hello, Richard. Could I ask you a few questions?
Of course! Is there something going on that I should know about?
Well, I've been trying to make friends with the other employees as you suggested. I was just wondering -- what's your relationship with Stan like?
Stan's a good friend of mine. He's been with us since the beginning and consistently turns in excellent work. I can't say I have any complaints. Why do you ask?
I was just wondering. Most of the employees don't seem to really love him.
I think he might be the culprit behind the gender discrimination mentioned in that note.
Well in my experience, he's a great asset to this company and an excellent friend. Try to get to know him, I'm sure he'll come around. Keep up the good work, Alex.
That's quite a serious accusation. Stan can be a bit... overbearing at times but I don't think he means any harm. Maybe try asking around some more. Thank you for letting me know Alex.
